{"tid":1526363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係好多怪獸家長","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:01:39.000Z","uid":53209,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1810666be1bd9862253bc288cdba656c0107337f","tid":1526363,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"小弟住屯門<br />\n<br />\n啱啱坐輕鐵出街食飯<br />\n咁有2個4/5歲大既細路<br />\n攞住個哨子係月台係咁必必吹<br />\n老豆老母就係到同2條細路講：「上左車就唔準吹架啦」<br />\n<br />\n係月台等車6分鐘 keep住吹足6分鐘<br />\n我到最後忍唔住 我望實佢 再望一望佢個仔 眼神示意<br />\n佢get到後就問我咩事 <br />\n我「你唔覺得咁樣好騷擾人？」<br />\n然後一副覺得室外地方無問題 佢吹咩係佢自由<br />\n<br />\n同佢鬧左幾分鐘 到最後佢地係某個公屋車站落左車<br />\n<br />\n有時 真係唔怪得人睇唔起 低質到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定其實係我太mean"},{"pid":"54df7dd13f5d94bc7cfe7e52a786dbca9d90f371","tid":1526363,"uid":82291,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"你知唔知什麼是怪獸家長？<br />\n你講既事只係一對無品家長"},{"pid":"e947794f13051c77a60676bed41c5b5b08f22ede","tid":1526363,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54df7dd13f5d94bc7cfe7e52a786dbca9d90f371","tid":1526363,"uid":82291,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"你知唔知什麼是怪獸家長？<br />\n你講既事只係一對無品家長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:43:32.000Z","msg":"明 咁我更正 無品"},{"pid":"621ebbef5eb03e455661107a62d3a8baaf2912f5","tid":1526363,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"香港人好多都唔正常"},{"pid":"14091c847f505acc1b577b5835db620e555f84ad","tid":1526363,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"621ebbef5eb03e455661107a62d3a8baaf2912f5","tid":1526363,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"香港人好多都唔正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"佢個仔真係慘"}]}